Description: Streamlines the creation of common charts by taking care of a lot of
    data preprocessing and plot customization for the user. Provides a
    high-level interface for creating plots using 'ggplot2'.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    colorspace,
    dplyr,
